Description: Quarto-based personal portfolio site for Mahmoodur Rahman,
    MD MPH MDS. Renders to a static GitHub Pages site. All content lives
    in data/portfolio_data.R; HTML is generated by box modules in modules/.
    Follows the research compendium structure of Marwick et al. (2018).
